---
title: Garlic Roasted Turkey and Creamy Dijon Sauce with Jewelled Wild Rice Pilaf and Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Roasted turkey dinner gets a sophisticated twist with a zippy cream sauce. Served with wild rice and Brussel's sprouts roasted to perfection; you won't want to wait for Sunday to make this dinner!
